      "name": "Creative Coding",
      "abstract": "Creative coding connects software, visual culture, sound, interaction, generative systems, education and experimental publishing.",
      "description": "Creative coding is the use of programming as an artistic, design or exploratory medium rather than only as an engineering implementation tool.",
